RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.4.5" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

Visit https://phy.wiki for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES in "1.4.5"
=========================

* Allow not to copy the localhost HOST catalog into the TARGET system
* Refactored localhost and template repositories and catalogs
* Added new support function bandit_source_repackage_top

